                <h1>Essential Background Checks for Substitute Teachers: Why They Matter</h1>
                <p>A background check for a substitute teacher is a crucial step to ensure the safety and well-being of students. This process typically includes criminal history evaluations, verification of past employment, and checks against child abuse registries. It's vital for schools to employ trustworthy substitutes to foster a secure learning environment.</p>
